{"tid":2361361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部駐港公署強烈譴責美英澳加外長聯合聲明","createTime":"2021-01-10T14:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T14:58:17.000Z","uid":291865,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f8652ade8e946033b7bf414a552d27252e47be1b","tid":2361361,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:39:08.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】外交部駐港特派員公署強烈譴責及堅決反對美英澳加外長聯合聲明。<br />\n<br />\n公署發言人指，聯合聲明公然違反國際法和國際關係基本準則，污蔑抹黑香港國安法；又指被捕人士絕不是他們粉飾美化的所謂「民主活動人士」，而是涉嫌顛覆國家政權，嚴重危害國家安全的犯罪分子。批評有關國家無視其本國密不透風的國安立法，一而再、再而三，惡毒攻擊香港國安法是典型的雙重標準，敦促他們認清歷史和現實，立即停止干預香港事務和中國內政。"},{"pid":"4bf313f3f93a3f33cf4cf733efdea155cc2e2e47","tid":2361361,"uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:40:14.000Z","msg":"召喚大和田"},{"pid":"5b153977261ba8b5ea775b57ff225464d4bc7d73","tid":2361361,"uid":340081,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4bf313f3f93a3f33cf4cf733efdea155cc2e2e47","tid":2361361,"uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:40:14.000Z","msg":"召喚大和田"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:45:47.000Z","msg":"成全你<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2DV3V4O.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2DV3V4O.gif&h=5e442bd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2da416f90382dadb81c86fa94b63e66cf2d1199d","tid":2361361,"uid":327169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:55:40.000Z","msg":"昂膠駐港豬員表示你班黑警真係要死全家!!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c31c830772e4b76242495344c193f2f7c25dc2","tid":2361361,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:58:17.000Z","msg":"向美利堅宣戰<br />\n向英吉列宣戰<br />\n向澳大利亞宣戰.jpg"}]}